# SIMURA OS — package manifest for the live/installer ISO.
#
# This file is consumed verbatim by archiso/mkarchiso. Each non-comment,
# non-blank line must be a single valid package name available in the
# configured pacman repositories ([core], [extra], [multilib]).

# --- Base system -------------------------------------------------------------
base
base-devel
linux
linux-firmware
linux-firmware-marvell
amd-ucode
intel-ucode
mkinitcpio
mkinitcpio-archiso
mkinitcpio-nfs-utils
syslinux
edk2-shell
grub
efibootmgr
dosfstools
