# --- Calamares installer (AUR / chaotic-aur, NOT in official repos) ---------
# These are pulled in at build time by scripts/build.sh from the AUR via
# `yay -S calamares` once it's running inside the container. For the
# initial bring-up build we skip them so the package list resolves.
# calamares
# ckbcomp
hwinfo
